{"tid":1596493,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[此風不可長] TSC 保養期內拒維修，屈入水呃錢","createTime":"2019-09-26T13:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T00:51:51.000Z","uid":284689,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f0105fcaa3d38e1cd621f250b6af8b95ca438b","tid":1596493,"uid":284689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"TSC 整機服務出左名垃圾，今次我帶你睇下到底有幾垃圾。文有少少長，唔想睇都要睇埋呢句：千奇唔好去TSC整機，就算整都唔好比佢屈錢！<br />\n本文底部有圖，如果你係記者朋友，歡迎你聯絡<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我隻AirPods右邊經常性充唔到電，Genius Bar最快都帶等幾日先有得整，TSC好多Appointment。單耳聽歌真係好辛苦，所以明知有伏都想試試TSC，去左銀城廣場的TSC整機。<br />\n<br />\n前台的CS 正正常常搵電筒照個充電盒後就交左比房入面的師傳check，然後：<br />\nCS：師傳話你隻AirPods個充電盒d金屬有dd氧化，即係入過水，要比$469先可以維修，而且要擺底幾日，無貨即刻換<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：我隻AirPods同盒無入過水，點可以當Liquid Damage?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCS：跟據Apple的指引，金屬氧化都會當係Liquid Damage。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我： 我隻AirPods重係保養期內，而且我肯定無入過水，擺係空氣都會有機會氧化啦，我會帶返去Apple整。不過我要投訴你地check機的師傳，因為我肯定Apple無呢個條款，而且唔會好似你地咁屈個客。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旁邊的CS：你攞去Apple佢地都唔會整，一樣會收錢，呢個係Apple的指引，你唔滿意可以打去Apple Care投訴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCS聽到投訴後要求我比隻AirPods的充電盒比房入面的師傳影相留個Record！我拒絕左，因為佢事前就可以影相，佢可以出嚟影。佢攞入房影的話，可以故意整滴水去我個充電盒度老屈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾日後，我去左Genius Bar整，Genius係我面前Check機，做左基本測試後確定問題，等左一陣就直接換充電盒，無提到有任何氧化或者液體損壞。//多謝Apple的 Genius，你地真係專業！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />//<br />\n<br />\n按Apple的定義：試水紙變色就當液體損壞。TSC所謂的金屬氧化＝液體損壞，指充電的金屬片有任何磨損都視作氧化，與Apple的判斷方式嚴重不同。結果，在保養期內的產品，TSC都照樣都會屈你out of warranty，然後屈你出錢比佢地整，千奇唔好上當。<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑TSC成日用呢招去屈d急住整機的人，又或者唔熟悉Apple Policy的人，所以想出文叫大家小心d，唔好上當。去TSC就算你唔整，都浪費車錢同時間，等多幾日去Apple整都好過上TSC被人屈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 識少少Apple人，亦算了解少少Apple的維修條款同作風。<br />\n問題： 有無其他巴絲有類似經歷？此風不可長，我打算去海關舉報下TSC不良營商手法欺騙顧客，歡迎一齊教導下TSC！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otRVOCm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotRVOCm.jpg&h=76b19c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9QSQQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9QSQQS.png&h=6d57dcfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c20f2d59e25092cf4e135accd8f67c6322f53a27","tid":1596493,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oq9Tz9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foq9Tz9f.jpg&h=dc0f42d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6d515ba73501dfd0acfe3eaea4ccbf6dc03d33e","tid":1596493,"uid":284689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cec43af784043befc50324bdcfe2d42ddccfc22","tid":1596493,"uid":284689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43880ac58752b9e08a8d466982f287cf6901809","tid":1596493,"uid":239086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"TSO係黑店唔係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e852c71c6ceb4a9b88d9bedf778030b080e6d815","tid":1596493,"uid":1089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"所有非原廠維修都係垃圾黎，特別係呢間TSO<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nApple products真係唔好因為難book而唔去Genius bar整"},{"pid":"9f463883c80a516205a36c3c8ba022c62b8634d7","tid":1596493,"uid":284689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43880ac58752b9