">TSO</span>成日用呢招去屈d急住整機的人，又或者唔熟悉Apple Policy的人，所以想出文叫大家小心d，唔好上當。去<span style=\"color: red;\">TSO</span>就算你唔整，都浪費車錢同時間，等多幾日去Apple整都好過上<span style=\"color: red;\">TSO</span>被人屈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 識少少Apple人，亦算了解少少Apple的維修條款同作風。<br />\n問題： 有無其他巴絲有類似經歷？此風不可長，我打算去海關舉報下<span style=\"color: red;\">TSO</span>不良營商手法欺騙顧客，歡迎一齊教導下<span style=\"color: red;\">TSO</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e313c74684f47da80c9be8f74af00cb5e4db87","tid":1596493,"uid":159413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post我醒起早兩日攞塊 ROG底板去整<br />\n佢話針腳有損就唔保要貼兩百換板<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱查完<br />\n官網寫左只要唔係故意刻意整爛都會保<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgecScS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgecScS.png&h=5d8ed284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYCqsMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYCqsMe.png&h=30fc517d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nASUS | 漢科電腦公司| Hornington Computers Company<br />\n<br />\n正仆街"},{"pid":"60e9bce1e936ceceae741c31582e5cc43ef38fee","tid":1596493,"uid":239086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e313c74684f47da80c9be8f74af00cb5e4db87","tid":1596493,"uid":159413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post我醒起早兩日攞塊 ROG底板去整<br />\n佢話針腳有損就唔保要貼兩百換板<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱查完<br />\n官網寫左只要唔係故意刻意整爛都會保<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgecScS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgecScS.png&h=5d8ed284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYCqsMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYCqsMe.png&h=30fc517d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nASUS | 漢科電腦公司| Hornington Computers Company<br />\n